getUserProperties

java.util.Map<java.lang.String,java.lang.String> getUserProperties()
Returns:
the properties defined by the user. It does not include the internal versionable implementation properties. The collection of properties returned are not modifiable. The keys and values in this map are considered opaque by the RTC server. URIs should not be placed in this map if the user/caller is expecting these URIs to be portable after data configuration. We do not provide any introspection on these values. This map should not be used for any identifiers which are not immediate attributes of this item. It is not recommended that these fields are used to store references to other items in the repository, as this could impact the state when it gets replicated to another repository.

Parameters:
